description: The user clicked on the "Properties" option in the desktop context menu.
outcome: A context menu opened, revealing options like "Arrange Icons By", "Refresh", "Paste", "New", and "Properties".  The mouse cursor, now a white arrow with a blue box, hovers over the "Properties" option.

description: The user clicked the highlighted "Properties" option in the desktop context menu. As a result, the context menu closed.
The user clicked on the "Screen Saver" tab at the top of the "Display Properties" window. As a result, the window's content switched from the "Themes" tab to the "Screen Saver" tab.
outcome: The user switched to the "Screen Saver" tab within a larger window or dialog. This tab allows customizing the screensaver type, wait time, and related settings. The previously visible "Theme" section and its associated controls are no longer present.

description: The user clicked the "Screen saver" dropdown menu and selected "Starfield".
outcome: The selected option in the "Screen saver" dropdown menu changed to "Starfield".

description: The user clicked on the "None" option in the "Screen Saver" dropdown menu. As a result, the dropdown menu closed, indicating "None" was selected as the screensaver.
outcome: The screen saver wait time was changed from 10 to 1, and the dropdown menu closed.

description: The user clicked the "Power..." button within the "Display Properties" window's "Screen Saver" tab. This action resulted in the "Power Options Properties" window appearing.
outcome: The appearance of the "Power Options Properties" window partially obscures the "Display Properties" window.  The mouse cursor changes to an hourglass, indicating system activity.

description: The user clicked the mouse on the "Turn off monitor" option's dropdown menu, causing the menu to expand and display a list of time options.
outcome: The 'Turn off monitor' option's dropdown menu expanded to display a list of time options, with the mouse cursor moving into the expanded menu area.

event: The mouse clicked on After 5 hours.
description: The user clicked on "After 5 hours" in the "Turn off monitor" dropdown menu within the "Power Options Properties" window. As a result, the dropdown menu closed, and "After 5 hours" became the selected option.
outcome: The "Turn off monitor" dropdown menu now displays "Never".

description: The user clicked the highlighted "OK" button in the "Power Options Properties" window.  As a result, the "Power Options Properties" window closed.
outcome: The 'Power Options Properties' window closed, revealing the previously obscured 'Display Properties' window beneath it.

description: The user clicked the "OK" button at the bottom of the "Display Properties" window, closing the window.
